works.description: The wooden "Simply Wood" logo shown on their website was stolen from ours (this is a previous version of our logo, before we added "Inc"  The domain name itself was also stolen, but that's a different story. I would like to start by getting their site out of your search results.

The photographs in the slideshow of the kitchens are our photographs of kitchens that we handcrafted; they are wrongly displaying our hard work and claiming it as their own.

Since this is a slideshow, I'll give direct links to the infringing images - you can also watch the slideshow on any of their pages and see these images rotate.
